00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:55,000
Have a taste of the porridge.

123
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,560
It's nice.

124
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:31,320
Guang, how does Ye Sirong behave

125
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,520
