226
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:54,120
Isn't that convenient?

227
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,920
Yes, it is.

228
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:58,600
"The merciful can't lead an army,
the kind can't hold wealth."

229
