00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:27,800
I realize

552
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:30,600
I don't know anything

553
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,680
apart from being a host.

554
00:35:33,240 --> 00:35:34,600
I'm just useless.

555
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:38,040
Xiaomeng, don't say that.

556
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:40,400
You just haven't found the right job.

557
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:42,760
When Uncle Zhou passed away,

558
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,480
didn't he leave you and your mother

559
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,480
some of the shares of Shenghai?

560
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:49,120
You can use that money
to start a business.

561
00:35:51,160 --> 00:35:52,760
I don't want to use Uncle Zhou's money.

562
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:55,760
And the shares are still frozen.

563
00:35:57,520 --> 00:35:58,360
I see.

564
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:01,200
If you need a job,
I can recommend you to someone.

565
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:02,960
There's no need.

566
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,600
I can figure this out.

567
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:07,480
I don't want help from any of you.

568
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:11,480
Look, you're as stubborn

569
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:13,120
as Zhou Yanzhao.

570
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:15,840
Then I can only wish you all the best.

571
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,040
What's wrong with A Yan?

572
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:20,000
Is he in trouble?

573
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,680
The proposal for Dikai Commercial City.

574
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,920
Your father's in charge of this project.

575
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,000
Is there anything wrong?

576
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:30,200
I'm moving to his team to help him.

577
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:36,640
So you're giving up on the projects
you're working on?

578
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,080
We have the same goal,

579
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:39,440
that is to work for Shenghai.

580
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:43,760
This project has high business value

581
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:45,360
and it's almost finished.

582
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:48,320
All that's left is asking for investments
and promotion.

583
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:49,840
I believe

584
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,720
if you and your father join hands,

585
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:54,080
that will go down well.

586
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:55,440
Of course.

587
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:58,720
So A Yan, you agree
that I move to Dikai project's team?

588
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,720
I have no reason to refuse.

589
00:37:01,200 --> 00:37:03,320
The Yunnan Resort project
is going smooth as well.

590
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,920
Given your ability,

591
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:06,440
I believe you can do well on both sides.

592
00:37:06,640 --> 00:37:08,040
No problem. Don't worry.

593
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:11,240
Besides, if you do well
in your father's team,

594
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:13,240
I can learn from you as well.

595
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:15,360
Jiang Ze,

596
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:17,000
I wish you all the success.

597
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,400
Thank you, A Yan.

598
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,560
But I have one more thing to say.

599
00:37:20,680 --> 00:37:21,480
Please.

600
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,800
From now on, if I ask Xiaomeng out,

601
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,160
please don't meddle with it.

602
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,080
Nothing.

603
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:44,080
It's just company business.

604
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:46,160
Just as I see you,

605
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:48,600
it instantly puts me in a better mood.

606
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,920
Xiaomeng, thank you.

607
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:55,880
You're like a sunbeam

608
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,240
that shines through the shadow
covering my eyes.

609
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:02,120
See? You called me artistic.

610
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,600
You sound like a crappy poet.

611
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,360
Crappy? Why crappy?

612
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:10,280
If not crappy, how about trashy?

613
00:38:12,720 --> 00:38:14,040
Why are you doing this hand gesture?

614
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,720
It's silly.

615
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,640
(Meeting)

616
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:24,920
What has Xiaomeng been doing
these two days?

617
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:26,680
She's looking for a job.

618
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:31,080
She never mentioned it to me.

619
00:38:32,920 --> 00:38:34,600
Yan, are we going home?

620
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,080
Let's go to the hospital.

621
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:39,480
Sure.

622
00:38:40,680 --> 00:38:41,840
Xiaomeng, get in.

623
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,400
I'll put the takeaway bag in the trunk.

624
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:59,000
Xiaomeng, why are you not getting in?

625
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:10,680
I'm sorry, Xiaomeng.

626
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,520
I didn't want you to know about this.

627
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:18,440
Jiang Ze...

628
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:21,960
thank you.

629
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:26,080
I'm worried that you'll get upset, so...

630
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:28,320
♪ A love too deep ♪

631
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:31,600
♪ Can easily make one sacrifice ♪

632
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:35,280
♪ Can easily make one sink ♪

633
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:38,200
♪ Can easily make one act recklessly ♪

634
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:40,680
♪ And fill one with scars ♪

635
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,520
♪ I'm too stupid ♪

636
00:39:42,600 --> 00:39:45,960
♪ I knew you aren't the right person ♪

637
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:49,720
♪ I know this isn't fate ♪

638
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:54,840
♪ But I still go ahead ♪

639
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,640
Mommy Lin,

640
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:01,920
will you be my mom forever?

641
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,880
Of course.

642
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:07,520
Not only you, all the kids in the center

643
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:08,920
are my children.

644
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,920
Do you have your own children?

645
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:20,480
Yes.

646
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,800
Mother Lin lost him...

647
00:40:26,080 --> 00:40:27,320
accidentally.

648
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,880
Mother Lin, if you don't find him

649
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:32,240
and he can't find his mother,

650
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,080
he must be very anxious.

651
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,920
Mother Lin, how did you lose him?

652
00:40:38,120 --> 00:40:38,920
I...

653
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:45,000
Aunt Lin.

654
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,440
A Yan, you're here.

655
00:40:52,160 --> 00:40:53,560
I bought a present for Tiankong.

656
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:56,400
Tiankong...

657
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,880
This is Uncle Zhou. Say hi to Uncle Zhou.

658
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:00,960
Hi, Uncle Zhou.

659
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:02,720
Thank you, Uncle Zhou.

660
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,080
Tiankong,

661
00:41:04,560 --> 00:41:06,280
"uncle" might be a bit confusing.

662
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:07,640
Like sister Xiaomeng,

663
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:08,720
you may call me brother A Yan.

664
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,360
Brother A Yan.

665
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,600
There you go.

666
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,480
He can't wait to take it.

667
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,320
Look what it is.

668
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:20,120
Thank you, brother A Yan.
I really like it.

669
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:22,160
How do you know that I like this?

670
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:25,040
Because I liked it when I was little.

671
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:29,440
So I thought all boys would like it.

672
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,960
Mother Lin, can I go to that open space

673
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,120
and play a little bit?

674
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,520
Of course you can. Have fun.

675
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:39,520
Mother Lin, but you haven't

676
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:41,680
told me how you lost your kid.

677
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:45,640
I...

678
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:49,040
I was just joking.

679
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:51,240
Go play over there.

680
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:57,600
This kid likes drawing

681
00:41:58,160 --> 00:41:59,560
so he's very imaginative.

682
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:02,760
His head is just full of strange thoughts.

683
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:05,960
Let's take a seat.

684
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,200
Here.

685
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:14,480
Aunt Lin,

686
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,040
have you seen Xiaomeng lately?

687
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:21,920
Not a lot.

688
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:24,840
I think she said she's looking a job.

689
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:27,880
What's wrong?
Is everything okay with you guys?

690
00:42:29,720 --> 00:42:32,360
Nothing, I'm just worried about her.

691
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:35,080
She doesn't tell me a lot of things.

692
00:42:36,080 --> 00:42:38,160
You actually really care about Xiaomeng.

693
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:40,280
It's just that when you two meet,

694
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:41,440
you can't deal with the feelings

695
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:43,680
you have for each other, right?

696
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:46,840
Yes, that's right.

697
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:49,600
A Yan, in your heart,

698
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:52,880
do you hate Xiaomeng a little bit?
